stream api-a sequence of element that can be proceed in a pipeline of operation such as filtering mapping
sorting and reducing

one operation output will be the input of another operation
streams dont store data anywhere it only perform operation and then you need to store it into a list manually

collection to stream -> Collection.stream()
array to stream -> Arrays.stream()
direct stream -> stream.of()

two extra method
stream.iterate()
stream.generate()

all stream api are divided into 2 parts 
intermidiate operation - filter, map, distinct, sort and limit